loads/2025/06/bungalow-cabin-architecture-170625-552-06-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bungalow-cabin-architecture-170625-552-06-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bungalow-cabin-architecture-170625-552-06-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bungalow-cabin-architecture-170625-552-06-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/bungalow-cabin-architecture-170625-552-06-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003ePathways and Walkways\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eElevated pathways weave through the trees like quiet forest trails, connecting each private bungalow without disturbing the land below. These walkways don’t just provide access, they encourage wandering. Made with locally sourced materials and designed to blend into the environment, they offer subtle views of the terrain, occasional glimpses of the rivers below, and the sounds of nature all around.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eRaised on slender pilotis, each walkway and platform allows rainwater, animals, and undergrowth to pass naturally beneath, preserving the delicate ground ecosystem that makes this canyon so special.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"960\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-01.jpg\" alt=\"A stone-clad jungle bungalow in Costa Rica blends effortlessly into its forest surroundings. A curved concrete path leads to the entrance, while a floating terrace and rich timber ceiling invite guests into a space that feels both grounded and elevated.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-01-940x470.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-01-800x400.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-01-768x384.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-01-1536x768.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-02.jpg\" alt=\"A stone-clad jungle bungalow in Costa Rica blends effortlessly into its forest surroundings. A curved concrete path leads to the entrance, while a floating terrace and rich timber ceiling invite guests into a space that feels both grounded and elevated.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-02.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-02-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-02-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-02-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-02-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-02-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-03.jpg\" alt=\"A stone-clad jungle bungalow in Costa Rica blends effortlessly into its forest surroundings. A curved concrete path leads to the entrance, while a floating terrace and rich timber ceiling invite guests into a space that feels both grounded and elevated.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-03.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-03-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-03-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-03-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-03-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2400\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-04.jpg\" alt=\"A raised walkway leading to a stone bungalow nestled in the Costa Rican forest. Elevated on slender pilotis, the structure floats above the ground, blending tropical modern design with lush, natural surroundings.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-04.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-04-940x1175.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-04-800x1000.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-04-768x960.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-04-1229x1536.jpg 1229w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-04-1638x2048.jpg 1638w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-05.jpg\" alt=\"A raised walkway leading to a stone bungalow nestled in the Costa Rican forest. Elevated on slender pilotis, the structure floats above the ground, blending tropical modern design with lush, natural surroundings.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-05.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-05-940x705.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-05-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-05-768x576.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/landscaping-pathway-170625-545-05-1536x1152.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2\u003eThe Interiors\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eInterior designer \u003ca href=\"https://saragovia.com\"\u003eDania Saragovia\u003c/a\u003e carried the architectural ethos indoors. Her warm, earthy palette feels rooted in place, while natural fibers and woven textures echo the surrounding jungle. It’s comfort without excess, each detail is intentional, every material aligned with the broader vision of calm and connection.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003ePrivate outdoor bathtubs and open-air terraces allow guests to bathe beneath the trees or sit quietly above the canyon. Inside, a single long window stretches across the room, perfectly framing the view and inviting the landscape to become part of the interior experience. A discreet divider between bedroom and bathroom maintains privacy without sacrificing openness.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-01.jpg\" alt=\"This warm, light-filled guest accommodation invites rest and relaxation. Sheer curtains, natural wood paneling and ceiling, and sculpted side tables create a calm, handcrafted feel, while the low bed and open layout make space for slow, restful moments.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-02.jpg\" alt=\"This warm, light-filled guest accommodation invites rest and relaxation. Sheer curtains, natural wood paneling and ceiling, and sculpted side tables create a calm, handcrafted feel, while the low bed and open layout make space for slow, restful moments.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-02-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-02-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-02-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/up