170625-527-06-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-06-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-06-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bedroom-living-room-170625-527-06-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1280\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-01.jpg\" alt=\"This serene bathroom pairs a floating concrete vanity with warm brass fixtures for a modern, spa-like feel. Vertical wood paneling adds natural texture, while soft daylight and clean lines create a calm, grounded atmosphere.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-01-940x627.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-01-800x533.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-01-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1707\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-02.jpg\" alt=\"This outdoor bath feels like a hidden retreat carved into nature itself. Rough-cut stone walls catch the shifting sunlight, casting textured shadows that dance across the scene. The deep soaking tub, with its sand-toned finish and exposed copper fittings, brings a raw simplicity that’s quietly elegant.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-02.jpg 1707w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-02-940x1410.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-02-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-02-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-02-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/small-cabin-design-bathroom-170625-527-02-1366x2048.jpg 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1707px) 100vw, 1707px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou can watch a short video of the project to see how the bungalows float above the forest and open up to breathtaking canyon views.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ciframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/djU59J2XwmI\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"\u003e\u003c/iframe\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eExplore the architectural drawings and see how the design takes shape on paper\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1242\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-01.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings of a treetop retreat in Costa Rica.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-01-940x608.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-01-800x518.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-01-768x497.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-01-1536x994.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"1242\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-02.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings of a treetop retreat in Costa Rica.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-02-940x608.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-02-800x518.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-02-768x497.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-02-1536x994.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1287\" height=\"833\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-03.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural drawings of a treetop retreat in Costa Rica.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-03.jpg 1287w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-03-940x608.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-03-800x518.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/architectural-drawing-170625-531-03-768x497.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1287px) 100vw, 1287px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Rio Perdido We